d</item></change><change n="meta.1447"><date>2009-03-20</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>253BC</date>
<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Προμηθίων Ζήνωνι χαίρειν. ἔγραψάς μοι περὶ τοῦ κηροῦ ὅτι 

    <lb n="2"/>καθίσταται τὸ <expan>τά<ex cert="high">λαντον</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num> σὺν τῶι τέλει τῶι κατὰ Μέμφιν <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="44">μδ</num>, σὺ δὲ ὅτι 

    <lb n="3"/>πυνθάνοιο εἶναι παρ᾽ ἡμῖν <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="40">μ</num>. μὴ οὖν πρόσεχε τοῖς ληροῦσιν, πωλεῖται 

    <lb n="4"/>γὰρ <del rend="erasure">παρ᾽ <choice><corr>ἡμῖν</corr><sic>ημε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied></sic></choice></del> ἐνταῦθα <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="48">μη</num>. <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κα</supplied>λῶς οὖν ποιήσεις ἀποστ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ίλας</supplied> ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="5"/>ὅσον πλεῖστον δύνηι. δέδωκα δὲ κα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">θ</supplied>άπερ μοι ἔγραψας Αἰγύπτωι τῶι 

    <lb n="6"/>παρ᾽ ὑμῶν εἰς τὴν τιμὴν τοῦ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ηροῦ</supplied> ἀργυρίου <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="500">φ</num>, <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αὶ</supplied> τὸ λοιπὸν δὲ ὃ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἂ</unclear>ν ἦι 

    <lb n="7"/>ὧι ἂν ἐπιστείληις διορθώσομαι παραχρῆμα. καὶ μέλιτος δέ μοι ληφθή<add place="supralinear">τω</add>σαν 

    <lb n="8"/><expan>με<ex cert="high">τρηταὶ</ex></expan> <num value="5">ε</num>. ἐπαινῶ δέ σου τὴν εὔνοιαν καὶ τὴν προθυμίαν ἣν <add place="supralinear">ἀεὶ</add> εἰς ἡμᾶς ἔχεις. 

    <lb n="9"/>καὶ σὺ δ᾽ ἐάν του χρείαν ἔχηις τῶν καθ᾽ ἡμᾶς, μὴ ὄκνει γράφειν. 

    <lb n="10"/>ἔρρωσο. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="33">λγ</num>, Φαρμοῦθι <num value="19">ιθ</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="11"/>Ζήνωνι. 

    <lb n="12"/>τὸ θέατρον οἰκ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">οδο</supplied>μῆσαι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.1447" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1447" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-253" notBefore="-253" type="textDate" value="-0253-06-10">10. Juni 253 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1447" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">5</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59823</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1447</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">5</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59823</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;5;59823" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1447" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Pl. V Recto</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.1447" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Thompson, Memphis under the Ptolemies (1988), S. 74</bibl><bibl type="translations">Meijer &amp; van Nijf, Trade, Transport and Society (1992), S. 67</bibl><bibl type="translations">Bagnall &amp; Derow, The Hellenistic Period (2004), Nr. 100.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="fr"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Orrieux, Les papyrus de Zenon (1983), S. 76</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.1447" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Mendes</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.1447" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DACTION/IPAPwebquery?vPub=P.Cair